reviewText: I purchased the DVD as a Christmas gift, and the recipient of the gift absolutely loved it and the quality of the DVD was excellent.

I love this CD! My favorites are tracks 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 8, and 12. And the DVD is even better.  You can dance with him on track 12 (Bishop Neal's Praise). All I can say is make room on your Ipod for this CD because there are a lot of gems on it.
